#: ../../source/user_guide/linear_solvers.rst:2
#: 1054686833ec45d98a3f68ff641e6f06
msgid "Sparse Solvers"
msgstr "稀疏求解器"

#: ../../source/user_guide/linear_solvers.rst:4
#: 15444327109744669f0ea2c87f0e3bc4
msgid ""
"After assembly and boundary-condition condensation you have a sparse system "
"— linear or nonlinear — to solve. TensorMesh delegates this work to `torch-"
"sla <https://www.torchsla.com/>`_, a standalone differentiable sparse-"
"linear-algebra library. The same FEM code retargets between CPU and GPU, and"
" between iterative and direct solvers, by changing one keyword argument; "
"nonlinear systems are driven by the same backend through a Newton / Picard /"
" Anderson interface."
msgstr ""
"完成装配和边界条件凝聚之后，你便得到一个待求解的稀疏系统——线性或非线性。TensorMesh 将这项工作委托给 `torch-sla "
"<https://www.torchsla.com/>`_\\ ，一个独立的可微稀疏线性代数库。同一份有限元代码只需改动一个关键字参数，即可在 CPU "
"与 GPU、迭代法与直接法求解器之间切换；非线性系统则由同一后端通过 Newton / Picard / Anderson 接口驱动。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/linear_solvers.rst:14
#: 3b39f80f44144ffebe219777abaa1d37
msgid "Install ``torch-sla``"
msgstr "安装 ``torch-sla``"

#: ../../source/user_guide/linear_solvers.rst:18
#: 9f1908845198460b81bbb824b4bb9d73
msgid ""
"``torch-sla`` is a **hard, import-time** dependency of "
":mod:`tensormesh.sparse`. The module will not import without it. It is also "
"the library where all current and future solver work lands — TensorMesh "
"tracks ``torch-sla`` releases as the canonical sparse-linear-algebra layer "
"and we recommend keeping it up to date."
msgstr ""
"``torch-sla`` 是 :mod:`tensormesh.sparse` 的\\ **硬性、导入期**\\ "
"依赖。缺少它该模块将无法导入。它同时也是当前及未来所有求解器工作落地的库——TensorMesh 将 ``torch-sla`` "
"的版本作为权威的稀疏线性代数层来跟随，我们建议保持其更新到最新。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/linear_solvers.rst:24
#: b2bb150424f44f0cb02ecc2da40133ab
msgid ""
"The base wheel ships the CPU stack (SciPy / native PyTorch). GPU backends "
"are opt-in extras — you can install one or both, depending on which CUDA "
"solver you want:"
msgstr ""
"基础 wheel 自带 CPU 栈（SciPy / 原生 PyTorch）。GPU 后端是可选附加项——你可以安装其中一个或两个，取决于你想使用哪种 "
"CUDA 求解器："

#: ../../source/user_guide/linear_solvers.rst:35
#: 2ffb7a7cccd34811af04b7247eada599
msgid ""
"TensorMesh also exposes the GPU extras at its own install layer (``pip "
"install \"tensor-mesh[cupy]\"`` etc.) — see "
":doc:`/getting_started/installation`."
msgstr ""
"TensorMesh 也在自身的安装层暴露了这些 GPU 附加项（\\ ``pip install \"tensor-mesh[cupy]\"`` "
"等）——参见 :doc:`/getting_started/installation`\\ 。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/linear_solvers.rst:40
#: 76ac2e3b2dcd41adac31ee97312ed55a
msgid "Inspect available backends"
msgstr "查看可用后端"

#: ../../source/user_guide/linear_solvers.rst:42
#: ed66567fedf14654a0d5ec630bb84329
msgid ""
"After installing, ``torch_sla.show_backends()`` prints a status table "
"showing which backends are usable on the current machine and how to install "
"any that are missing:"
msgstr ""
"安装完成后，\\ ``torch_sla.show_backends()`` 会打印一张状态表，显示当前机器上哪些后端可用，以及如何安装尚缺失的后端："

#: ../../source/user_guide/linear_solvers.rst:57
#: 0299c864d17549c689ab195e288fd716
msgid "What ``torch-sla`` gives TensorMesh:"
msgstr "``torch-sla`` 为 TensorMesh 提供了什么："

#: ../../source/user_guide/linear_solvers.rst:59
#: b40942f361b14ce98ff8d018cfee3373
msgid ""
":class:`~tensormesh.sparse.SparseTensor` — the COO data type that "
":class:`~tensormesh.sparse.SparseMatrix` extends. Element assembly hands you"
" a :class:`~tensormesh.sparse.SparseMatrix` directly, so every operator "
"method on the parent class (``@``, ``.solve``, ``.nonlinear_solve``, "
"``.is_symmetric``, …) is available without any extra wrapping."
msgstr ""
":class:`~tensormesh.sparse.SparseTensor` —— "
":class:`~tensormesh.sparse.SparseMatrix` 所继承的 COO 数据类型。单元装配会直接交给你一个 "
":class:`~tensormesh.sparse.SparseMatrix`\\ ，因此父类上的所有算子方法（\\ ``@``\\ 、\\ "
"``.solve``\\ 、\\ ``.nonlinear_solve``\\ 、\\ ``.is_symmetric`` "
"等）都无需任何额外包装即可使用。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/linear_solvers.rst:64
#: e378ecaa32ac4892a222d06c6c41044f
msgid ""
"A unified ``solve`` op with a custom backward pass (an adjoint sparse "
"solve), so gradients flow through every linear system."
msgstr "一个带有自定义反向传播（伴随稀疏求解）的统一 ``solve`` 算子，使梯度能够穿过每一个线性系统。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/linear_solvers.rst:66
#: 342679978ffe4cddaeb4926a80bb6957
msgid ""
"A pluggable backend layer covering CPU, GPU, iterative and direct solvers "
"behind a single dispatch entry point."
msgstr "一个可插拔的后端层，在单一分派入口点之后涵盖 CPU、GPU、迭代法与直接法求解器。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/linear_solvers.rst:71
#: 999aaa15b2b34b648a78fbc5c2067bdb
msgid "Solving ``A x = b``: the ``.solve()`` method"
msgstr "求解 ``A x = b``\\ ：\\ ``.solve()`` 方法"

#: ../../source/user_guide/linear_solvers.rst:73
#: f77fd24815c3445e8ea9df1a8e130211
msgid ""
"The canonical entry point is ``SparseMatrix.solve`` — inherited unchanged "
"from ``torch_sla.SparseTensor``. Assembly already returns a "
":class:`~tensormesh.sparse.SparseMatrix`, so this is the only call you "
"normally need:"
msgstr ""
"权威入口点是 ``SparseMatrix.solve`` —— 原封不动地继承自 ``torch_sla.SparseTensor``\\ "
"。装配本身就已返回一个 :class:`~tensormesh.sparse.SparseMatrix`\\ ，所以通常你只需要这一个调用："

#: ../../source/user_guide/linear_solvers.rst:84
#: a6b01b5060b442ec973c6ea28a328330
msgid ""
"**Symmetry / positive-definiteness is auto-detected.** On every call, "
"``torch-sla`` computes ``is_symmetric()`` and ``is_positive_definite()`` on "
"the matrix, then picks CG / Cholesky for SPD systems and BiCGStab / LU "
"otherwise. You do **not** pass an ``is_spd`` hint; passing one would be "
"ignored."
msgstr ""
"**对称性 / 正定性会被自动检测。** 每次调用时，\\ ``torch-sla`` 都会对矩阵计算 ``is_symmetric()`` 和 "
"``is_positive_definite()``\\ ，然后为对称正定（SPD）系统选用 CG / Cholesky，否则选用 BiCGStab /"
" LU。你\\ **不需要**\\ 传入 ``is_spd`` 提示；即便传入也会被忽略。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/linear_solvers.rst:90
#: 09a9aa5a939d40efa1375f02dc5dd302
msgid "Key keyword arguments (full list in the ``torch-sla`` reference):"
msgstr "关键关键字参数（完整列表见 ``torch-sla`` 参考文档）："

#: ../../source/user_guide/linear_solvers.rst:92
#: 5436d7114ad543ef9b13ad207ce7a230
msgid ""
"``backend``: ``\"auto\"`` (CPU → SciPy, CUDA → cuDSS when available, else "
"CuPy / native PyTorch), or one of ``\"scipy\"``, ``\"eigen\"``, "
"``\"pytorch\"``, ``\"cupy\"``, ``\"cudss\"``."
msgstr ""
"``backend``\\ ：\\ ``\"auto\"``\\ （CPU → SciPy，CUDA → 可用时为 cuDSS，否则为 CuPy / "
"原生 PyTorch），或是 ``\"scipy\"``\\ 、\\ ``\"eigen\"``\\ 、\\ ``\"pytorch\"``\\ 、\\"
" ``\"cupy\"``\\ 、\\ ``\"cudss\"`` 之一。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/linear_solvers.rst:95
#: a55f66a81b984e30844f15cda349783b
msgid ""
"``method``: ``\"auto\"`` (chosen from matrix properties + backend), or an "
"iterative method (``\"cg\"``, ``\"bicgstab\"``, ``\"minres\"``, "
"``\"gmres\"``, ``\"lgmres\"``) or a direct factorization (``\"lu\"``, "
"``\"umfpack\"``, ``\"cholesky\"``, ``\"ldlt\"``). Not every backend supports"
" every method — see the table below."
msgstr ""
"``method``\\ ：\\ ``\"auto\"``\\ （根据矩阵性质 + 后端选择），或某种迭代法（\\ ``\"cg\"``\\ 、\\ "
"``\"bicgstab\"``\\ 、\\ ``\"minres\"``\\ 、\\ ``\"gmres\"``\\ 、\\ "
"``\"lgmres\"``\\ ），或某种直接分解法（\\ ``\"lu\"``\\ 、\\ ``\"umfpack\"``\\ 、\\ "
"``\"cholesky\"``\\ 、\\ ``\"ldlt\"``\\ ）。并非每个后端都支持每种方法——参见下表。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/linear_solvers.rst:100
#: 9e29245839194d4ebf63f6e404e8bfc7
msgid ""
"``atol`` (default ``1e-10``), ``tol`` (default ``1e-12``), ``maxiter`` "
"(default ``10000``) for iterative convergence."
msgstr ""
"``atol``\\ （默认 ``1e-10``\\ ）、\\ ``tol``\\ （默认 ``1e-12``\\ ）、\\ ``maxiter``\\"
" （默认 ``10000``\\ ），用于迭代收敛。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/linear_solvers.rst:102
#: 2994178c2f89483dbb2756af20985c68
msgid ""
"``verbose=True`` prints a one-line summary of the auto-selected backend / "
"method and the detected matrix properties — handy when you want to confirm "
"that ``\"auto\"`` picked the path you expected:"
msgstr ""
"``verbose=True`` 会打印一行摘要，给出自动选择的后端 / 方法以及检测到的矩阵性质——当你想确认 ``\"auto\"`` "
"是否选中了你预期的路径时非常方便："

